1. Installed NVM using:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Closed the terminal and reopened it.

3. Installed Node.js v20.16.0:
   nvm install 20.16.0
   nvm use 20.16.0

4. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 using npm:
   npm install sass@3.7.4

5. Confirmed installation with:
   npx sass --version
